INFO.name: QUERY
INFO.value: SELECT TOP 5000 RAJ2000, DEJ2000, e_RAJ2000, e_DEJ2000, gmag, e_gmag, rmag, e_rmag, imag, e_imag, Ng, objID FROM "II/349/ps1" WHERE 1=CONTAINS(POINT('ICRS', RAJ2000, DEJ2000), BOX('ICRS', 254.325542, 71.833139, 0.483, 0.483)) AND gmag IS NOT NULL AND rmag IS NOT NULL AND imag IS NOT NULL AND rmag <= 20.0
